{"tid":2048357,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消防工會反對加入特務警察　管方發信批評斥挑撥分化 追究到底","createTime":"2020-06-02T17:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T08:12:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"83154342eef251d8f82f1b6c68baec3ce179afd5","tid":2048357,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T17:52:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200602/ZIOS5YZJQQVFFTD7IXGBZM7NA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FZIOS5YZJQQVFFTD7IXGBZM7NA4%2F&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgerkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=2f5dd85f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FZIOS5YZJQQVFFTD7IXGBZM7NA4%2F&h=910fb6b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200602/ZIOS5YZJQQVFFTD7IXGBZM7NA4/</a><br />\n<br />\n消防處近月以非公開方式招募逾百名部門人員加入「特務警察」，做法引起部門內外非議。消防處今日（2日）傍晚向部門人員發信，解釋參考過其他部門經驗和因涉敏感資料，終選擇內部推薦而非公開招募。處方同時批評新消防工會在事件中與政府立場背道而馳，聲言若發現有人故意製造事端，「抹黑」或「誣衊」部門或同事，令部門形象或聲譽受損，「定必採取適當行動，追究到底」。新工會表示反映同事看法是履行職責，希望管方尊重。"},{"pid":"d92194bf63c07b4f83adc4e8b9d707900c0d77c8","tid":2048357,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T17:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5448945eb22d0fca9b6baaa0a211969e1746a0b5","tid":2048357,"uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T18:00:01.000Z","msg":"內部推薦 = 想奶先要奶袋底，你想跟中共搵食呀 ? 交學費未 ?"},{"pid":"b000c1b510b65b3c899972f4247b15619c35614b","tid":2048357,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5448945eb22d0f